_______________________________________
ATTENTION STUDENTS:
McGraw Hill is a service provider to your educational institution.
Requests about personal information collected and processed in connection with a course at your school
must be submitted by an authorized school administrator.
Please contact the office of the Registrar or Dean of Students and request that they submit this form on your behalf.
_______________________________________
Privacy Request Form
Click
here
to unsubscribe from e-mail marketing.
For all other requests regarding personal information collected and processed by McGraw Hill, submit this form.
After you submit the form, you will receive an email with instructions for verifying your identity. Your request will not be processed until your identity has been confirmed.
By completing and submitting this request, you authorize McGraw Hill to contact you for the purposes of responding to your request. Information entered into this form will only be shared with third parties as required to process your request.
For more information about how we collect and process your personal information, please visit the
McGraw Hill Privacy Center
.
How may we help you today?
